 />\n<br />\n界王自己學到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果北界王教哂無限，天津飯用界王拳<br />\n咁力量大會就唔洗驚啦"},{"pid":"9e8562efa7ddde64780742f2e19f18cd65227fff","tid":182234,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實人類學唔學到界王拳？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n界王自己學到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果北界王教哂無限，天津飯用界王拳<br />\n咁力量大會就唔洗驚啦</blockquote><br />\n我見到果刻仲係到諗我幾時回過呢個po"},{"pid":"4cfae2a01292df11c67b7b83a30eed4f372384e6","tid":182234,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"大家好似唔記得界王拳係有副作用"}]}